  "body": "Hi there,\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version:  1.8.2-stable\r\nArchitecture:  amd64\r\nProtocol Versions: [63 62]\r\nGo Version: go1.10\r\nOS & Version: Centos-7\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nserver-side:\r\ngeth --syncmode=light --rpcaddr \"172.21.1.231\" --rpc --rpcvhosts=\"london-node-231.tamama.london\"\r\n\r\nclient-side:\r\ngeth attach https://london-node-231.tamama.london:28546\r\n\r\n\r\nExpected behavior : Geth console should show up.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\n[root@london-node-231 ~]# geth attach https://london-node-231.tamama.london:28546\r\nFatal: Failed to start the JavaScript console: api modules: Post https://london-node-231.tamama.london:28546: x509: certificate signed by unknown authority\r\n\r\n",
